The [[Wise Old Man]] can assign various tasks on [[member]] worlds and give small rewards in return. 

The most common tasks are to fetch between 3 and 15 of one of the following items (this list may not be exhaustive). They can be brought in more than one load. The Wise Old Man doesn't accept [[Bank note|bank notes]], as they have no use to him.

